snippet.title: ►Colton Haynes&Amber Heard | Crazy Kids [+Marcel♥]
snippet.description:
WATCH IN HD! ♥
______________________________

"cause that's just who we are."

Tweet this to Colton Haynes? Pleaseee :D

#CAMBER ♥ (go and check out our banners on youtube,lol ^^) YESSS! We ship these two as hell xD I mean look at them... they could be a perfect couple! :D Anyways Marcel is obssesed with Colton as much as I am with Amber sooo yeahhh this is like our little ship that we found today :3 Ofcourse his parts are way better than mine since i don't do picture videos,hahahah xD and we finished this in one day ^^  Don't forget to comment&leave opinion what you think. :)

Subscribe Marcel here;
http://www.youtube.com/user/ItsCassyBiatch

I started the collab and he finished it :)

I did Amber and he did Colton :D
"Hey guys it's Colton Haynes"
"Eating it's a talent. It's my best talent."
"Hi, it's Amber Heard."
"Get out of the shot!"
"My Dad actually tried to give me a gun."
"I got you a pretty one."
"I will always love you! That was acting..."
